36#include "krb5_locl.h"
37
38KRB5_LIB_FUNCTION krb5_error_code KRB5_LIB_CALL
39krb5_free_kdc_rep(krb5_context context, krb5_kdc_rep *rep)
40{
41 free_KDC_REP(&rep->kdc_rep);
42 free_EncTGSRepPart(&rep->enc_part);
43 free_KRB_ERROR(&rep->error);
44 memset(rep, 0, sizeof(*rep));
45 return 0;
46}
47
48KRB5_LIB_FUNCTION krb5_error_code KRB5_LIB_CALL
49krb5_xfree (void *ptr)
50{
51 free (ptr);
52 return 0;
53}
